    <div class="container abt-desc">
        <h1 class="text-center p-5">About GO USETECH</h1>
        <div class="row pb-5 myflex">
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <div class="abt-text">
                    <h5>Welcome to GO USETech - Empowering Futures Through Technology</h5>  
                    <p>                        
                        At GO USETech, we believe in the transformative power of education and technology 
                        to create opportunities for all. We are a non-profit organization dedicated to making 
                        quality education accessible to everyone, regardless of background or circumstance.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="pt-2">Who We Are:</h5>
                    <p class="">
                        GO USETech is more than an educational platform; we are a community-driven initiative committed 
                        to empowering individuals through technology. As a registered non-profit organization, we operate 
                        with a mission to bridge gaps and create a future where everyone can thrive in the digital age.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="pt-2">Our Mission:</h5>
                    <p>
                        Our mission is to provide inclusive, tech-driven education that goes beyond traditional boundaries. 
                        We aspire to empower individuals with skills that not only open doors to new opportunities but also 
                        contribute to building a more inclusive and digitally literate society.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="pt-2">Our Commitment:</h5>
                    <p>
                        GO USETech is fully registered with the government, ensuring transparency, accountability, and 
                        adherence to the highest standards. By choosing GO USETech, you're not just enrolling in a program; 
                        you're joining a movement dedicated to empowering futures through technology.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="pt-2">Get Involved:</h5>
                    <p>
                        Whether you're a student eager to learn, a professional seeking to upskill, or someone looking to make 
                        a difference, GO USETech invites you to be a part of our community. Together, let's embrace the boundless 
                        possibilities of education and technology.
                    </p>
                    <h5 class="pt-2">
                        Join us in this exciting journey of empowerment, where every learner is a catalyst for positive change.
                    </h5>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-lg-6 col-md-12">
                <img 
                    class="img-responsive" 
                    src="/images/gousetech42.jpg"
                    width="500"
                    height="480"
                >
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="gray-bg">
        <div class="container projects pb-5">
            <div class="text-center p-5">
                <i class="fa fa-project-diagram"></i>
                <h2 class="sect-header">Our Projects</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="project-grid">
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech22.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt="IT skills training image"
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>IT Skills Training Program:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Implement a comprehensive IT skills training program that 
                                covers computer literacy, Microsoft Office proficiency, 
                                graphics design, video editing, web development, programming, 
                                and other relevant IT skills. The program can be structured 
                                in modules or courses and delivered through workshops, classes, 
                                or online platforms.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech23.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Digital Literacy Workshops:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Conduct workshops to enhance digital literacy among refugees, 
                                covering topics such as internet usage, online safety, email 
                                communication, social media, and online job searching. 
                                This project would focus on building foundational digital 
                                skills that are essential in today&#39;s digital world.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech31.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Mentorship and Career Guidance:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Establish a mentorship program where IT professionals 
                                volunteer their time to provide guidance and support to 
                                refugee participants. Mentors can offer career advice, 
                                share industry insights, provide networking opportunities, 
                                and help refugees navigate their IT career paths.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive"
                            src="/images/gousetech21.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Data and Research Capacity Building using KoBoToolbox:</h4>
                            <p>
                                By offering this project, GO USETECH continues to expand its mission 
                                of empowering individuals and organizations with vital digital skills 
                                while emphasizing the importance of data literacy and research expertise 
                                in the modern world.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech38.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>IT Internship and Job Placement Program:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Develop partnerships with local businesses, IT companies, 
                                and organizations to secure internships and job placement 
                                opportunities for trained refugees. This project would 
                                focus on bridging the gap between training and employment, 
                                providing refugees with valuable work experience and a 
                                pathway to sustainable employment.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech33.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Community IT Centers:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Establish community IT centers in areas with a high 
                                refugee population, providing a safe and supportive 
                                space for refugees to access IT resources, receive 
                                training, and engage in community activities. These 
                                centers can serve as hubs for learning, collaboration, 
                                and integration.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech01.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>IT Entrepreneurship Support:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Offer support and resources for refugees interested in
                                starting their own IT-related businesses. This could 
                                include training in entrepreneurship skills, access to 
                                microloans or grants, and mentorship from successful IT 
                                entrepreneurs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech53.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Digital Skills for Women Empowerment:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Design and implement specific projects focused on 
                                empowering refugee women through IT skills training, 
                                addressing gender disparities and promoting women&#39;s 
                                inclusion and participation in the tech industry.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="project">
                    <div class="card">
                        <img 
                            class="img-responsive" 
                            src="/images/gousetech46.jpg" 
                            width="" 
                            height=""
                            alt=""
                        >
                        <div class="p-2">
                            <h4>Tech for Social Impact:</h4>
                            <p>
                                Encourage refugees to leverage their IT skills for social 
                                impact by supporting projects that address social and 
                                humanitarian challenges. This project would involve 
                                identifying and supporting innovative tech-based solutions 
                                that benefit refugee communities and address their 
                                specific needs.
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="container pb-5">
        <div class="text-center p-5">
            <i class="fa fa-key"></i>
            <h2 class="sect-header">Our Core Values</h2>
