                                    lives, build self-confidence, and pursue their aspirations.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Inclusivity:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We value inclusivity and strive to create an environment that
                                    respects and embraces diversity, fostering a sense of belonging 
                                    and equal opportunities for all refugees, regardless of their 
                                    backgrounds or circumstances.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Collaboration:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We recognize the importance of collaboration and actively seek
                                    partnerships with like-minded organizations, educational 
                                    institutions, industry professionals, and local communities to 
                                    create a collaborative ecosystem that maximizes our impact and 
                                    resources.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Innovation:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We embrace innovation and stay abreast of emerging technologies 
                                    and trends, continuously adapting our training programs to meet 
                                    the evolving needs of refugees in the digital age.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Empathy:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We approach our work with empathy, recognizing the unique challenges 
                                    faced by refugees. We provide a supportive and compassionate learning 
                                    environment that values individual experiences and promotes holistic 
                                    growth.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Accountability:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We are committed to being transparent and accountable in all our 
                                    actions and decisions. We adhere to the highest ethical standards, 
                                    ensuring responsible use of resources, and measuring our impact to 
                                    drive continuous improvement.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <div class="text-right">
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-12 col-md-12 col-sm-12">
                                <i class="fa fa-quote-left pb-2"></i>
                                <h4 class="">Social Impact:</h4>
                                <h5 class="px-5">
                                    We are driven by a deep commitment to creating positive social 
                                    change. Our focus is on equipping refugees with IT skills that 
                                    have the potential to transform their lives, foster community 
                                    development, and contribute to the overall well-being of society.
                                </h5>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#core-carousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
              <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Previous</span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#core-carousel" data-bs-slide="next">
              <span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
              <span class="visually-hidden">Next</span>
            </button>
          </div>
        </div>
